reviewText:
ITS ABOUT BEARDED MAN FISTING A BEAR,

No really it does;

Okay, its a very simple beat'em up game where you have a very tight control of punching and kicking mechanic. Duration is short and very repetitive as most of bear and boss bear have the same fighting movement only with different health. Lack of combo due to only have punching, kicking and stomping is very dissapoint so does the level interaction. The game solely sold base on its humor rather than it gameplay.So if you like bear joke then your are welcome. Graphic-wise its pixelly and with good choice of colour.
